            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/mouse-from-fumi-game/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 07:50:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mouse]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[独立游戏]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210483</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>波兰独立游戏工作室 Fumi Game 开发的复古射击游戏《Mouse》日前上传了早期游玩示范影片，让玩家以第一人称投身 1930 年代黑白卡通世界。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210513" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-7-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-7-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-7-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-7-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-7-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-7-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="MOUSE Early Gameplay Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4KoNDAW4JrE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210517" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-30-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-30-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-30-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-30-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-30-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-30-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210518" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/mousegame-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/mousegame-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/mousegame-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/mousegame.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《Mouse》是一款 Noir 黑色风格的 FPS 射击游戏，其独特视觉风格灵感源自 1930 年代的经典卡通，将玩家带回 20 世纪 30 年代的橡皮管动画（Rubber Hose Animation）世界。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-10-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-10-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-10-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-10-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-10-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-10-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>游戏中玩家会扮演出一名私家侦探，在一个充满帮派、流氓的城市中探索。玩家可以在这个混乱、腐败和充满活力的黑色城市中利用各种武器、能量道具和爆炸物追求正义，阻止腐败的政客继续掌管这个城市。游戏的武器非常有玩味，而且生命值显示非常独特，配上卡通人物般的敌人，为传统 FPS 游戏带来一抹轻松的风景。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210515" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-44-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-44-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-44-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-44-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-44-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-44-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210516" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-46-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-46-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-46-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-46-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-46-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/MOUSE-Early-Gameplay-Trailer-0-46-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Fumi Game 在 Steam 表示，《Mouse》预计将于 2025 年发行。</p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4KoNDAW4JrE&amp;ab_channel=FumiGames">Fumi Game@YouTube</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2416450/Mouse/">Steam</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/mouse-from-fumi-game/game-channel/">《Mouse》发布游戏示范影片，波兰独立开发 1930s 黑白卡通风格 FPS</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
