        <item>
            <title>玩家沉迷 Steam Deck 散热位气味   Valve：气体无害但不要再闻</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/steam-deck-smell/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=steam-deck-smell</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/steam-deck-smell/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 07:49:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[steam]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[steam deck]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Steam Deck OLED]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Valve]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1209799</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>相信许多人都喜欢一些「奇怪」的气味，例如停车场、油站，甚至是收据的气味，但近日外国有一名玩家喜欢的气味就更加「奇怪」，他爱上的是 Steam Deck 散热排气口散发的味道，其后更询问 Valve 官方这样闻 Steam Deck 是否安全。</p><p>Steam Deck 顶部设有散热孔，游玩时内置风扇会转动，以排出热气，帮助 Steam Deck 散热。有部分玩家似乎开发了奇怪的癖好，游玩时刻意将鼻子贴近排气口，尽情享受 Steam Deck 的独有味道。</p><p>由于电子产品内部零件甚多，因此无法确定这些零件运作时温度升高后会否产生对人体有害的物质，所以 Reddit 一名玩家 <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Metapod100/">@Metapod100</a> 专诚向 Valve 查询，到底「吸 Steam Deck」 是否安全。Valve 官方回应指， Steam Deck 正常运作时排放的气体没有安全问题，但仍不建议玩家主动吸入电子设备排出的气体。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/i-asked-valve-about-sniffing-the-vent-and-v0-aa1bicg8hw5c1-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/i-asked-valve-about-sniffing-the-vent-and-v0-aa1bicg8hw5c1-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/i-asked-valve-about-sniffing-the-vent-and-v0-aa1bicg8hw5c1-416x900.jpeg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/i-asked-valve-about-sniffing-the-vent-and-v0-aa1bicg8hw5c1.jpeg 739w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/i-asked-valve-about-sniffing-the-vent-and-v0-aa1bicg8hw5c1-710x1536.jpeg 710w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/SteamDeck/comments/18grijh/i_asked_valve_about_sniffing_the_vent_and/?rdt=48448">Reddit</a></p><p>除了 @Metapod100 外，外国也有不少玩家表示喜欢 Steam Deck 散热口排出的味道。X（前称 Twitter）上就有网友 @SirLarr 表示他闻过 Steam Deck 的味道后发觉非常好闻。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">I just huffed the new electronics fumes directly from the Steam Deck&#39;s vent.</p><p>That&#39;s goooood shiiiiiitttttt</p><p>&mdash; Lawrence Sonntag (@SirLarr) <a href="https://twitter.com/SirLarr/status/1539396062628020225?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">June 21, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>除此之外， Reddit 上亦有网友 @oxelhare 表示他已经 44 岁了，但每次闻到 Steam Deck 排气口的味道时也会觉得自己像是回到 12 岁般样。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210502" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕撷取画面-2023-12-14-132917-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕撷取画面-2023-12-14-132917-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕撷取画面-2023-12-14-132917-768x501.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕撷取画面-2023-12-14-132917.jpg 823w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/SteamDeck/comments/14bkhr8/comment/joh69ka/">Reddit</a></p><p>厂商永远不可以低估游戏玩家的「创意」。早前 Nintendo 推出 Switch 之时，为了避免儿童误吞 Switch 游戏卡带，Nintendo 刻意在卡带涂上世界上已知最苦的化合物：苯甲地那铵。这种苦味剂的苦度会苦到令人产生阴影。据 Yahoo 新闻报道指，如果奎宁的苦度是 1 的话，苯甲地那铵的苦度达 1000。尽管如此，仍然有不少玩家会刻意尝试 Switch 卡带。</p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://kotaku.com/valve-steam-deck-fumes-vent-smell-good-safe-exhaust-1851094071">kotaku</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=260674">巴哈姆特</a>、<a href="https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/61589/valve-ask-not-to-huffing-steam-deck-vent-fume">4Gamers</a>、<a href="https://tw.news.yahoo.com/switch%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E7%89%87%E6%9C%83%E8%8B%A6-%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%A1%97%E4%BA%86%E9%80%99%E6%9D%B1%E8%A5%BF-104557587.html">Yahoo 新闻</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/steam-deck-smell/game-channel/">玩家沉迷 Steam Deck 散热位气味   Valve：气体无害但不要再闻</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/steam-deck-smell/game-channel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>《Call of Duty》官方制裁外挂玩家，多人模式一用这把枪即死</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/call-of-duty-mw3-ban-hacker/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=call-of-duty-mw3-ban-hacker</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/call-of-duty-mw3-ban-hacker/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 07:48:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Call of Duty]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210561</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小编闲时很喜欢玩多人游戏，但如果场内有外挂玩家的话，会严重影响到游戏体验。最近《Call of Duty Modern Warfare 3》多人游戏模式出现大批外挂玩家，拿着本来只供 DMZ 模式使用的雷射枪周围胡作非为，严重破坏守法玩家的游戏体验。官方昨日（13 日）宣布，以后在多人游戏模式使用雷射枪的玩家一开枪就会「被自杀」。</p><p>《Call of Duty Modern Warfare 3》玩家 <a href="https://twitter.com/txtyy_">@txtyy_</a>上周在 X（前称 Twitter）上传了一段游戏影片。影片中可见 @txtyy_ 多次被雷射枪「秒杀」，下面有网友亦表示感同身受，并分享相似的经历。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">silent aim and a raygun, games chalked <a href="https://t.co/jlU4IbZmoF">pic.twitter.com/jlU4IbZmoF</a></p><p>&mdash; ⛧ (@txtyy_) <a href="https://twitter.com/txtyy_/status/1733309656578076892?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 9, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210564" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕撷取画面-2023-12-14-175924-694x371.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="371" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕撷取画面-2023-12-14-175924-694x371.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕撷取画面-2023-12-14-175924-1280x684.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕撷取画面-2023-12-14-175924-768x410.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕撷取画面-2023-12-14-175924-1536x820.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/萤幕撷取画面-2023-12-14-175924.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲@txtyy_ 被雷射枪秒杀的场景，图片来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/txtyy_/status/1733309656578076892">txtyy_@X</a></p><p>雷射枪实际上是 DMZ 模式中出现的武器，本来就不是设计予玩家在多人模式使用。《Call of Duty》官方今晨（13 日）在 X 发文表示由今日起，所有在多人模式中使用雷射枪的外挂玩家，一开枪就会立即「被自杀」。官方发文后很多玩家在下面回应额手称庆。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://game.udn.com/game/story/122089/7638320">udn</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/call-of-duty-mw3-ban-hacker/game-channel/">《Call of Duty》官方制裁外挂玩家，多人模式一用这把枪即死</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/16/call-of-duty-mw3-ban-hacker/game-channel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
